text: The 1966–1967 Algerian Championnat National was the fifth season of the Algerian Championnat National since its establishment in 1962. A total of 16 teams contested the league, with CR Belcourt as the defending champions. ==Team summaries== === Promotion and relegation === Teams promoted from Algerian Division 2 1966-1967 * USM Bel-Abbès * JSM Skikda Teams relegated to Algerian Division 2 1967-1968 * USM Blida * SCM Oran ==League table== ==References== ==External links== *1966–67 Algerian Championnat National Category:Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 1 seasons Category:1966–67 in Algerian football Algeria
title: 1966–67 Algerian Championnat National
